  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested creation of a structured prompt for Replit to develop a shopping comparison app. The app would feature product search, identification, comparison of 5+ similar products, price analysis for European sourcing, and Swiss delivery optimization. Manus created a comprehensive development prompt incorporating all requested features with industry best practices.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wanted to leverage Replit for developing a sophisticated shopping comparison application with specific focus on European markets and Swiss delivery\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nCreated a detailed, structured development prompt for Replit covering all requested features including product search, AI-powered query enhancement, comparison tables, filtering capabilities, and Swiss delivery optimization\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [development_prompt] Replit Shopping App Development Prompt — Comprehensive structured prompt for building a shopping comparison app with product discovery, comparison features, and Swiss delivery focus\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Include AI-powered natural language processing for product search\n- Focus on European sourcing with Swiss delivery optimization\n- Implement mobile-first responsive design approach\n- Integrate multiple API sources for comprehensive product data\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Structured prompt approach for complex app development\n- Clear feature specification\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Importance of market-specific optimization (Swiss delivery)\n- Need for intelligent query enhancement in product search\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Which specific e-commerce APIs should be integrated?\n- How to handle product data quality and consistency across sources?\n- What are the specific Swiss delivery requirements and constraints?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Implement the prompt in Replit environment\n- Test product search and comparison functionality\n- Integrate European e-co